<!DOCTYPE html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Arlex</title>
    <link href="/public/stylesheets/index.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">

    <!-- Bootstrap CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- Fontawesome CDN -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.3.1/css/all.css"
          integrity="sha384-mzrmE5qonljUremFsqc01SB46JvROS7bZs3IO2EmfFsd15uHvIt+Y8vEf7N7fWAU" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- jQuery integration -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/public/js/script.js"></script>

    <!-- Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">
    <!-- header -->
    <div class="row sticky-top navpage">
        <div class="col-lg-1 mx-auto">
            <a class="dashboardtitle" id="link-arlex">Description</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-1 mx-auto">
            <a class="dashboardtitle" id="link-notre-equipe">Notre équipe</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-1 mx-auto">
            <a class="dashboardtitle" id="link-contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-1 mx-auto">
            <a class="dashboardtitle" id="link-faq">FAQ</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid description center">
            <h1 class="arlex-title">Arlex</h1>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
                <img src="/public/jpg/logo.png">
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
            <h4 class=" arlex-text">Arlex permet à un déficient visuel de gagner du temps et de l’autonomie dans sa cuisine en demandant à un
                assistant vocal où se trouve un produit, ou bien avoir accès à ses informations comme la date de
                péremption, les ingrédients ou les allergènes. Tout cela sera rendu possible grâce à des capteurs qui seront
                installés dans les placards de la cuisine, ainsi que des patchs sur les produits.</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid notre-equipe center">
        <div class="mx-auto">
            <h1 class="notre-equipe-title">Notre Équipe</h1>
            <div class="row maxheightphotos">
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/benjamin.losson.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Benjamin Losson</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/charles.castelain.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Charles Castelain</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/simon.bauchet.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Simon Bauchet</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/corentin.minne.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Corentin Minne</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/augustin.lopacinski.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Augustin Lopacinski</figcaption>
                </figure>
                <figure class="offset-lg-1">
                    <img src="/public/jpg/orlane.oddo.jpg" class="rounded-circle" alt="">
                    <figcaption>Orlane Oddo</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid contact center">
        <div class="mx-auto">
            <h1 class="contact-title">Contact</h1>
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="/" method="post" data-toggle="validator">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Name *" value="" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Email *" value="" required/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <input type="text" name="subject" class="form-control" placeholder="Objet *" value="" required/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <textarea name="txtMsg" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Message *" required style="width: 100%; height: 150px;"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mx-auto form-group">
                    <button type="submit" value="Send Message" > Send Message</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="row-fluid faq center">
        <div class="mx-auto">
            <h1 class="faq-title">FAQ</h1>
            <div class="col-sm-6 mx-auto">
                <a onclick="open('first')">How do I change my password?</a>
                <div id="first" style="display: none">
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Quae quidem blanditiis delectus corporis, possimus officia sint sequi ex tenetur id impedit est pariatur iure animi non a ratione reiciendis nihil sed consequatur atque repellendus fugit perspiciatis rerum et. Dolorum consequuntur fugit deleniti, soluta fuga nobis. Ducimus blanditiis velit sit iste delectus obcaecati debitis omnis, assumenda accusamus cumque perferendis eos aut quidem! Aut, totam rerum, cupiditate quae aperiam voluptas rem inventore quas, ex maxime culpa nam soluta labore at amet nihil laborum? Explicabo numquam, sit fugit, voluptatem autem atque quis quam voluptate fugiat earum rem hic, reprehenderit quaerat tempore at. Aperiam.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    function open(div) {

        if (document.getElementById(div).style.display==="none") {
            document.getElementById(div).style.display="block";
        }
        else {
            document.getElementById(div).style.display="none";
        }
    }
</script>
</body>